3.2 ORGANIZATION PATTERN
--------------------------

Android Material 3 Guidelines recommend:
- GROUPED SECTIONS with dividers (not flat list)
- Group headings for related settings
- Most important/frequently used settings at top
- "Advanced" section only when 3+ items to hide
- Switches for binary options (inline, no separate screen)
- Menus for multiple-choice options
- Sliders for range values

