4.2 MULTIPLE AUTH METHODS
---------------------------

Best practice patterns:
- Show connected providers as a list with connect/disconnect buttons
- Require at least ONE auth method to remain connected
- Warn before disconnecting the last provider
- Email+password always available as fallback
- Social login icons: Google, Apple, GitHub (for dev users)
- For UNJYNX with Logto: supports 30+ providers, show most popular 3-4

Navigation pattern (from research):
  Profile icon (tab bar) > Profile header > Edit Profile button > Form
  OR
  Settings > Account > Profile > Edit

